{
  "stem": "5795.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He wouldn't allow her to eat at the table.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Even when I went there two years later, he wouldn't-- she-- he wouldn't allow her to sit at the table.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Anyhow, I said look, I'm coming every Friday night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I'll bring you food because I've got to eat too, and I'm not gonna have your rations, but I want the baby to be there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I said, I'm not coming anymore, and you're not gonna get any more food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So I sent my truck, and the following week, she was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The third, fourth week, she still wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I couldn't send my truck anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There was a Canadian boy, and he said-- as I wrote her later, I said, get your commanding officer to-- to give you permission to bring the baby, which she did eventually.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That kid-- no, her sister was here with her husband about two months-- two months ago.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And right then, we moved on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We moved on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Other's fancy stories, moving-- moving stories, fanciful stories, incredible stories in Holland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we moved on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I said to-- as we were moving into Germany, I said, I'm going back to Holland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm not doing any work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I visited a hospital, and I saw the non-Jewish chaplain dishing out, distributing cookies, razor blades, cigarettes, socks, all sorts of things, you know, in a big basket.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, where'd you get this from?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, well, you're at HQ, the welfare officer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I go back to the welfare and said, why can't I get any?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's only for hospital chaplains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we Jews cover everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We haven't got enough men to cover hospitals alone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he gave me.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
